<LI><P>Berry, Wendell.  1989.  &#147;The futility of global thinking,&#148; <I>Harper&#146;s Magazine</I>, September: 16-19, 22.</P>
<LI><P>Berry, Wendell.  1995.  &#147;Community In 17 Sensible Steps,&#148; <I>Utne Reader</I>, March/April: 17.</P>
<LI><P>Berry Wendell.  1995.  &#147;Conserving Communities,&#148; <I>Orion</I>, Summer: 49-49-53.</P>
<LI><P>Bray, Charles W.  1996.  &#147;Fostering Sustainable Community,&#148; <I>Wingspread Journal</I>, Issue 2 Spring: 3.</P>
<LI><P>&#147;Building for the Twenty-First Century: Industry&#146;s Role in the New Culture,&#148; <I>Northwest Report</I>, January 1996: 29-33.</P>
