<H3><A NAME="On-Line"></A> On-Line Bibliographies</H3>
<UL>
<LI><P>&#147;A Bibliography of &#147;Green&#148; Books<BR><A HREF="http://www.clas.ufl.edu/anthro/activism/green-bib.html">http://www.clas.ufl.edu/anthro/activism/green-bib.html</A>
