<P>Offers a five-unit course in sustainable living titled "Caretakers of the World."  The course consists of 22 half-hour lessons, from both introductory and advanced levels.  Contents describe environmental changes affecting air, water, and earth and the changes caused by fire.



<P><BR><BR><P><B>Global Learning, Inc.<BR>
