<html><head><!-- This document was created from RTF source by rtftohtml 
version
2.7.2 --><title>SCOTTSDALE ARIZONA CITYSHAPE 2020</title></head>
<BODY BGCOLOR = #FFFFFF> 
<A HREF="/index.html">
<IMG SRC="/rsc/photow8.gif" alt="= CESD 
