<P>PLATINUM-GROUP METALS. J. Roger Loe-benstein in <I>Mineral Facts and Problems</I>, U.S. Bureau of Mines Bulletin No. 675, U.S. Department of the Interior. U.S. Government Printing Office, 1985.

<P>THE MAKING, SHAPING, AND TREATING of STEEL. Edited by William T. Lankford, Jr., et al. Association of Iron and Steel Engineers, 1985.

