<title>Nature's Power on Demand</title>

<h2>Nature's Power on Demand:<br>
Renewable Energy Systems as Emergency Power Sources</h2>

<I>U.S. Department of Energy<br>
Office of Energy Efficiency and Renewable Energy<br>
October 1995<br></I>

<p><IMG SRC="/rsc/mrule.gif"><p>

