http://www.sustainable.doe.gov:80/ss/Common_Roots.html 205.168.79.33 19970115071947 text/html 9466
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 07:19:53 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Thu, 07 Nov 1996 15:33:01 GMT
